OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FAnd STV's senior management faced
OL,8,Fhostile questioning at a Scottish
OL,9,Fparliament committee.
OL,11,FIronically it seems to be the two
OL,12,Fbroadcasting unions which are taking a
OL,13,Fslightly more nuanced approach.
OL,15,FThe NUJ and BECTU are both strongly
OL,16,Fopposed to the proposals and fighting
OL,17,Ffor their members' jobs. If compulsory
OL,18,Fredundancies start to look likely, this
OL,19,Fcould become an industrial dispute. The
OL,20,Fproposed editorial changes have been
OL,21,Fbranded cultural vandalism by them.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
