OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FIn short, it only has a limited scope
OL,8,Fto impose loss-making legal obligations
OL,9,Fon STV. The value of a Channel 3
OL,10,Flicence is not what it was.
OL,12,FMy guess is a compromise.
OL,14,FSome form of sub-opt will stay. Perhaps
OL,15,F10 minutes dedicated to the Central and
OL,16,FNorth areas within the 6pm programme
OL,17,Fand dedicated bulletins at 10.30pm.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
