OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FThe examples elsewhere appear to
OL,8,Fsuggest that Ofcom would have no issue
OL,9,Fwith production and presentation in
OL,10,FGlasgow.
OL,12,FNobody would pretend that the north of
OL,13,Fscotland will get a better local
OL,14,Fservice as a result. But is it the best
OL,15,Fthat can realistically be afforded?
OL,17,FHow might STV (which made a loss and is
OL,18,Fbarely worth #50m) react if Ofcom
OL,19,Fthrows out its plans completely?
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
